    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Siegebreaker is a fast-paced tower defense game where every decision matters. Confront the might of four corrupted gods across handcrafted maps, and adapt your strategy with unique towers, meaningful upgrades, and powerful synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by the last benevolent deities, you are a divine construct—the final defense in a world of magic and chaos, now consumed by corrupted gods. Place your defenses with care, and unlock upgrades that fundamentally alter how your towers behave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/86689ba82f967cc31a6b6c7c387b7ea5.avif?t=1746734205\" width=616 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover over 40 unique upgrades and enhancements. Combine them to craft powerful builds and inventive strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/799bffafd0cb492c60e3fa60c67cb550.poster.avif?t=1746734205\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/799bffafd0cb492c60e3fa60c67cb550.webm?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/799bffafd0cb492c60e3fa60c67cb550.mp4?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/a85492526be8472fd03bb3bb34f6481f.avif?t=1746734205\" width=616 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tower can be upgraded to dramatically alter its behavior. Leverage synergies to maximize your effectiveness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/55c4c8e9f9d4dda9a41daf87cfeff787.poster.avif?t=1746734205\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/55c4c8e9f9d4dda9a41daf87cfeff787.webm?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/55c4c8e9f9d4dda9a41daf87cfeff787.mp4?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/e4ea7179826c4e39073d0491cddce434.avif?t=1746734205\" width=616 height=85 /></span><br>Balance your offensive and defensive capabilities to keep your towers protected against swarms of lethal enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/489882bb86e9b1a406dd256e4ec0840a.poster.avif?t=1746734205\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/489882bb86e9b1a406dd256e4ec0840a.webm?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/489882bb86e9b1a406dd256e4ec0840a.mp4?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/89f6e59c13a6fe11df0e3b1cc4bf8eb2.avif?t=1746734205\" width=616 height=85 /></span><strong></strong><br>Forge your path to victory by overcoming the challenges ahead in 25+ handcrafted levels across diverse environments- from the forests of Aethryn, deserts of Eranakis, frozen peaks of Haedmyr, and hellfire and Bal'Volar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/2ef087228e94e1941628fefbc5746b72.poster.avif?t=1746734205\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/2ef087228e94e1941628fefbc5746b72.webm?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146430/extras/2ef087228e94e1941628fefbc5746b72.mp4?t=1746734205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
